name: Whatthefoo
body: I couldn't justify driving to Chicago, but St. Paul was well within my driving range. Hopefully I can get plenty of sleep the night before in order to stay up past 8:30 on Saturday, August 22nd since the Foo Fighters concert doesn't start until 7:00 . . . and you and I will be there.
